    "Researchers often prioritize understanding the biological significance of a predictive model over its accuracy, requiring careful processing and correlation with existing biological knowledge.",
    "Bridging collaboration gaps between omics researchers, data scientists, and agricultural experts is vital for realizing the full potential of AI in plant defense and practical applications.",
    "Integration of AI and Omics Data in Early Disease Detection: One promising future direction is the seamless integration of AI with various omics data (genomics, transcriptomics, proteomics, and metabolomics) to enable the early detection of plant diseases.",
